    "content": "Creating a project on Leadhive is the first step to finding the right service provider for your property needs. We'll guide you through the process to ensure you get the best matches.\n\n<Note variant=\"info\">\n  Well-detailed projects typically receive faster and more accurate provider matches. Take time to include all relevant information.\n</Note>\n\n## Project Basics\n\nStart by providing the essential details:\n\n- Project title and category\n- Property location and type\n- Timeline and budget range\n- Service requirements\n- Project scope\n\n## Detailed Description\n\nHelp providers understand your needs by including:\n\n- Specific service requirements\n- Property details and conditions\n- Access information\n- Special considerations\n- Preferred timeline\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"Project creation form\"\n  src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/r-6-yk-gGPtjfbIST9-8uA/create-project/public\"\n  width={1200}\n  height={675}\n/>\n\n## Adding Photos\n\nInclude relevant photos to help providers assess your project:\n\n- Current property condition\n- Areas needing attention\n- Specific problem areas\n- Reference images (if applicable)\n\n<Note variant=\"success\">\n  Projects with clear photos receive 3x more responses from qualified providers.\n</Note>\n\n## Setting Preferences\n\nSpecify your preferences to get better matches:\n\n- Service provider requirements\n- Budget expectations\n- Timeline flexibility\n- Communication preferences\n- Required certifications\n\n## Review and Submit\n\nBefore submitting, double-check:\n\n- All required information is complete\n- Photos are clear and relevant\n- Budget range is realistic\n- Timeline is clearly stated\n- Contact details are correct\n\nReady to find your ideal service provider? [Create your project](/) now.",
